#: ../../docs/tutorials/shading/advanced_postprocessing.rst:27
msgid "The depth buffer cannot be accessed"
msgstr "深度バッファにアクセスできません"

#: ../../docs/tutorials/shading/advanced_postprocessing.rst:28
